text:
Great service ,
great cocktails good value for money. Thank you

Small and intimate safe space for the LGBTQ community. Amazing service from Kat and Norjan , resident DJ Farhan spins tunes that will keep you dancing throughout the night. The best bar on club street period 🌈🏳️‍🌈🥰

My go to bar when I’m in Singapore. The friendliness, inclusivity and family feels is what I get every time I come. I feel very safe here in my own identity and everyone is so warm here. Every trip this year, I am here because I feel so comfortable and the service from the bar manager and bartender are super amazing. They are super accommodating and lovely that I can only rave about this place
Super friendly and accommodating staff here! (: Nice, cosy place. Cocktail is tasty, and the popcorn chicken is amazing. 🤤
You can smoke and drink here and in Singapore that feels priceless. The host staff are incredible ❤️☺️
